## Known Issues & Resolutions

| Issue | Root Cause | Resolution |
|---|---|---|
| Gearbox shoulder joint failure | Repetitive load reversal | Redesigned with reinforced bracket |
| MPU6050 noisy readings | Flapping vibration | Foam tape anti-vibration mount |
| ESC cutout at high throttle | Exceeded 30A rating | Throttle limited to 70% |
| Wing spar resonance at max throttle | Standing wave mode | Avoid throttle >85% |
| Drift in roll (uncontrolled axis) | Wing asymmetry (weakened spar) | Replaced wing spar |

